    "description": "If you're a passionate Risk Analyst with drive and ambition, ET Money Ventures Solutions in Pune is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout ET Money Ventures Solutions:\nET Money Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Flexible working hours\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with ET Money Ventures Solutions!",
